label: A2B3_tI10_139_e_ae-001
title: Au$_{2}$Nb$_{3}$ Structure
comments:
(Schubert, 1960) listed the lattice constants in ``kX'' units.  We used the conversion factor 1.00207789 to convert their units into {\AA}ngstroms (Arblaster, 1997). (We had previously (Hicks, 2021) divided instead of multiplied.  This has been corrected.) 
 When $c/a = 5, z_{2} = 1/5$ and $z_{3} = 2/5$, the atoms are on the sites of a \href{current_web_home_dir/A_cI2_229_a-001}{body-centered cubic lattice}.
